      review: ["Validate quote/menu versioning, order transitions, timer durability, courier fencing, payment uncertainty, and ledger reconciliation.", "Exercise merchant outage, menu spike, courier shortage, duplicate webhook, late events, and full market failover."],
      takeaways: ["The order state machine and its deadlines are the cross-party coordination contract.", "Browsing tolerates stale projections; checkout, money, and assignment require authoritative revalidation and idempotency."],
