      questions: ["Which content types, domains, authentication modes, and recrawl freshness classes are in scope?", "What robots, Retry-After, legal, geographic, and per-publisher bandwidth rules apply?", "Should raw bodies be retained, and how are JavaScript rendering and crawler traps handled?"],
      functional: ["Discover, normalize, deduplicate, prioritize, and schedule URLs for initial and repeat fetch.", "Resolve DNS, enforce robots/politeness, fetch conditionally, parse links, and fingerprint content.", "Store fetch artifacts/status and expose replayable outputs to indexing or analytics consumers."],
