      mvp: ["Direct campaigns, contextual targeting, fixed priority/CPM, PostgreSQL control plane, Redis counters, CDN creatives, and Kafka events.", "Implement immutable approvals, signed impressions, bounded budget overshoot, no-ad fallback, and daily reconciliation."],
