      multiRegion: ["Distribute signed immutable snapshots globally; allocate campaign budget leases to cells based on forecast demand.", "Serve locally during partitions until leases expire, and route policy emergency denies on an independent global control channel."],
      cost: ["Serving CPU, feature retrieval, event transport, model inference, and reporting scans dominate; prune early and sample non-billable telemetry.", "Higher budget accuracy requires smaller/more frequent leases, increasing control traffic and stranded capacity."],
